WATCH NOW - CHOOSE TO MAKE A STATEMENT



 Gwen Stefani Chooses Super Lustrous Lipstick








DESCRIPTION





                    Make a statement with the world’s most iconic lipstick. Super Lustrous™ is formulated with microfine pigments for high-impact color. The smooth, moisturizing formula is available in 82 on-trend shades and four finishes – crème, matte, pearl and sheer.
                




FEATURES





                    •	NEW SHADES!
•	Micro-fine pigments for bold, rich color
•	Smooth moisturizing feel
•	82 classic & on-trend shades
•	Available in four finishes: crème, matte, pearl, and sheer
                




