Revlon International Corporation: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 9:25 AM ET
Personal Products

Company Overview of Revlon International Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Revlon International Corporation develops and markets cosmetics, skin, and personal care products. The company’s products include lipsticks, shampoo, eye shadow, mascara, conditioners, blush ons, and skin creams. It markets its products under Colorstay, Revlon Age Defying, Skinlights and Ultima II, Almay Kinetin, , Eterna 27, Ultima II, Jeanne Gatineu, Charlie, High Dimension, Flex, Mitchum, Colorsilk, Jean Nate, and Bozzano. The company was incorporated in 1963 and is based in New York, New York. Revlon International Corporation operates as a subsidiary of Revlon, Inc.


